| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3127 — Recovery Inhibition (funksec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0eaa1a69-4b8a-5f2d-aa60-fb21717e8339"
